indings for countries at different stages of the epidemic\nwith stable or unstable behaviors and increasing or decreasing numbers of\nconfirmed cases. Our results indicate that meta-projections can aid researchers\nin assessing the appropriateness of their relevant models and in effect\ndecrease the uncertainty in their estimations of an epidemic's severity and\ndevelopment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 26 Apr 2020 14:47:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-28"}
